OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,F- A further 700 roles are expected to
OL,7,Fclose across corporate divisions.
OL,9,F- All divisions will make significant
OL,10,Fsavings; some compulsory redundancies
OL,11,Fare likely, though they'll try to avoid
OL,12,Fthem. Voluntary redundancy windows are
OL,13,Fopening (more today).
OL,15,F- Some programmes will be closed.
OL,17,F- Commissioning spend across Content,
OL,18,FNews and Nations to be cut by c. #80m
OL,19,Fin 2027 ` 28.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
