OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,F- Broadcast TV channels and radio
OL,7,Fnetworks to be reviewed as audiences
OL,8,Fshift online.
OL,10,F- Senior leadership to be reduced by at
OL,11,Fleast 10%.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
