OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,GMORE DETAIL
OL,8,FMore information about the first round
OL,9,Fof cuts at BBC News was shared this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,12,FProgramme closures: BBC Radio 4 will
OL,13,Fclose The World Tonight, the Midnight
OL,14,FNews (at the end of the year), Money
OL,15,FBox Live, AntiSocial, The Law Show and
OL,16,FCrossing Continents; from April 2027
OL,17,Fthe 10pm slot becomes a domestic
OL,18,Fbulletin plus a simulcast of the World
OL,19,FService's Newshour. The World Service
OL,20,Fwill also close The Inquiry, The
OL,21,FConversation and The Fifth Floor by
OL,22,Fyear-end.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
