OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,FSchedule changes: BBC One will drop the
OL,7,FSunday edition of BBC Breakfast from
OL,8,FSeptember (replaced by a News channel
OL,9,Fsimulcast); the Friday edition of
OL,10,FNewsnight moves to a BBC Two peak-time
OL,11,Fslot; and 5 Live Weekend Breakfast
OL,12,Fextends to two hours from April.
OL,14,FTeam mergers: Sunday with Laura
OL,15,FKuenssberg and Newsnight combine; News
OL,16,FStreaming joins the News at Six and
OL,17,FNews at Ten team; some weekend TV
OL,18,Fproduction will be shared; and the News
OL,19,Fchannel will shift to a more
OL,20,Finternational agenda in an effort to
OL,21,Fraise global revenue.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
