OL,3,GNEWSCCuts being communicated to BBC
OL,4,CNews personnel today
OL,5,
OL,6,FPresenter and staffing reviews: Chief
OL,7,Fpresenter and on-air editor roles are
OL,8,Funder review. The Today programme drops
OL,9,Fto four presenters with a single anchor
OL,10,Fon Saturday. The BBC also plans fewer
OL,11,Flinear correspondents and crews,
OL,12,Fprioritising digital and mobile output.
OL,14,FGlobal: services in Africa will be
OL,15,Frestructured and some European roles
OL,16,Fclosed, despite a three-year World
OL,17,FService funding settlement.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
